comments: Favorite teacher by far. Meet with her in her office and she makes sure you understand everything. Doesn\'t waste time with the confusing text in the book. Just tells you how it is and skips the BS.

Best professor of all time. Not only does she help prep you for the huge citation exam at the end of each semester, she prepares you to the fullest for the stupid huge legal writing final. She walks you through everything necessary for papers, etc. Great professor, pray you get her.
My favorite professor so far and most helpful class.

Professor Donahoo is one of the best professors I have ever had. She is willing to help, but not give you the answer. I have learned so much from her class. If you go to class and pay attention (don\'t need to read) and actually try... then you will do well. I don\'t know what the person below is talking about, she is fair. Very good professor.

Learned nothing. Sarcastic and insulting to my classmate. Give grades on kissing up curve. lies to class about their chances. IF she likes a guy, she will send him flirty emails. She talks trash about students to students. School should man up and can her. She could be a good teacher if she wanted, but she doesnt want. You will think wour doing wel

She was a great professor in LP 1, probably the best any law school has but for LP 2 she just didn\'t seem to care. She didn\'t give us any direction then yelled at us for not doing what she wanted! Watch out in LP2, the curve may knock you down a grade! She is a real nice lady, always available to help and answer questions.

If you get on her bad side you are SOL; she definitely plays favorites. She really doesn\'t explain what she wants nor does she give examples. She may be something to look at but she is rather lacking in regards to her teaching. I\'d recommend switching to another LP class.
Best LP Prof at school. Thank your stars if ya get her! Soooo C U T E !!!

nice lady. bad powerpoints. hurried communication style. not much patience for questions. seems to be lenient with the guys & their questions & problems v. the girls. overall not a bad professor but not overly helpful. much of the class material will be self-taught & the writing will be hit & miss until you get what she\'s really looking for.
She\'s hot and knows it. She also knows the subject. Do the assignments/participate and you\'ll get a good grade.

Very nice and helpful. Wants you to learn and will do a lot to make that happen. The class it self isn\'t tough as long as you do what is asked of you. As far as attendance goes, being a guy I didn\'t have a problem because she\'s eye candy.
Hot as anyting.... loved to go to that class just to see her... WOW and she is an amazing prof. who has actual experience not bad... TAKE HER
